1
00:00:01,334 --> 00:00:02,769
-Benedict, you are starring in
"The Grinch".

2
00:00:02,769 --> 00:00:04,203
And as the Grinch,
it's your job

3
00:00:04,203 --> 00:00:05,938
to always look
grumpy and annoyed.

4
00:00:05,938 --> 00:00:07,473
-Yes.
-Take a look at this camera here

5
00:00:07,473 --> 00:00:09,041
and give us your best Grinch.

6
00:00:09,041 --> 00:00:10,443
Side by side. Yeah.

7
00:00:10,443 --> 00:00:12,645
Two.

8
00:00:12,645 --> 00:00:14,014
Yeah!

9
00:00:14,014 --> 00:00:15,982
-That's a good --
That's a good Grinch.

10
00:00:15,982 --> 00:00:17,583
[ Cheers and applause ]

11
00:00:17,583 --> 00:00:19,485
So, I thought I would put
your Grinch to the test

12
00:00:19,485 --> 00:00:22,255
by taking you on the
"Try Not to Laugh" challenge.

13
00:00:22,255 --> 00:00:24,590
We're gonna take turns
watching funny videos.

14
00:00:24,590 --> 00:00:26,826
And you have to keep
your best Grinch face...

15
00:00:26,826 --> 00:00:28,461
-Okay.
-...while trying not to laugh.

16
00:00:28,461 --> 00:00:30,663
-My Grinch resting face.
Here it comes.

17
00:00:30,663 --> 00:00:32,264
-You can go first, actually.
So...

18
00:00:32,264 --> 00:00:33,866
-Okay, yeah.
-I'm psyched 'cause I can laugh.

19
00:00:33,866 --> 00:00:35,235
Okay. Benedict, you go first.

20
00:00:35,235 --> 00:00:36,602
Ready?
-[ Breathes deeply ]

21
00:00:36,602 --> 00:00:39,239
-Watch that monitor. Let's play
the first video there.

22
00:00:44,677 --> 00:00:46,880
[ Cheers and applause ]

23
00:00:48,815 --> 00:00:51,184
[ Laughter ]

24
00:00:56,489 --> 00:00:58,858
-[ Speaks indistinctly ]

25
00:00:58,858 --> 00:01:00,560
-All right, here we go.
My turn.

26
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:02,929
-All right, good luck.
Good luck to you.

27
00:01:02,929 --> 00:01:05,298
[ Laughter ]

28
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:09,035
-[ Laughs ]

29
00:01:11,838 --> 00:01:15,241
What? I don't understand
what I just saw.

30
00:01:15,241 --> 00:01:18,344
Wait, what did I just see?
I have no idea what's happening.

31
00:01:18,344 --> 00:01:19,545
Was that ice?
-That was ice.

32
00:01:19,545 --> 00:01:21,481
That was someone trying
to get to their car.

33
00:01:21,481 --> 00:01:23,249
[ Laughter ]

34
00:01:23,249 --> 00:01:25,184
-He got hit by the other car?
Oh, my gosh.

35
00:01:25,184 --> 00:01:26,219
-Not what you think
is gonna happen.

36
00:01:26,219 --> 00:01:27,387
-Why would I laugh at that?

37
00:01:27,387 --> 00:01:28,954
No, no, no.

38
00:01:28,954 --> 00:01:30,656
All right, so far
we're zero for zero.

39
00:01:30,656 --> 00:01:31,858
Okay, it's your turn.
-All right.

40
00:01:31,858 --> 00:01:33,893
Whew.

41
00:01:35,762 --> 00:01:37,831
[ Laughter ]

42
00:01:39,532 --> 00:01:41,901
-Ooh.

43
00:01:43,036 --> 00:01:45,071
He did it! Oh, my God!
Look at that.

44
00:01:45,071 --> 00:01:47,974
He did it!
That's -- That's good.

45
00:01:47,974 --> 00:01:50,476
Tunnel vision. Tunnel vision.

46
00:01:50,476 --> 00:01:52,044
-All right.
All right, here we go.

47
00:01:52,044 --> 00:01:53,612
-English classical...training.
-My turn. Here we go.

48
00:01:53,612 --> 00:01:55,314
[ Clears throat ]
No training at all.

49
00:01:55,314 --> 00:01:58,051
-Straight off the streets.
Go on, do it, Jimmy.

50
00:01:58,051 --> 00:01:59,886
-Yep.
[ Farting noise ]

51
00:01:59,886 --> 00:02:01,955
[ Laughter ]

52
00:02:07,526 --> 00:02:10,463
-You had a much, much
tougher challenge.

53
00:02:10,463 --> 00:02:13,133
That was so
straight out of the gate.

54
00:02:13,133 --> 00:02:15,068
I had no idea.
Ready? [ Fart noise ] No.

55
00:02:15,068 --> 00:02:19,038
I wasn't ready.
He certainly wasn't ready.

56
00:02:19,038 --> 00:02:24,010
-Wait, what?
Can we see that one again?

57
00:02:24,010 --> 00:02:25,511
[ Fart noise ]

58
00:02:25,511 --> 00:02:27,213
[ Laughter ]

59
00:02:30,216 --> 00:02:31,918
[ Fart noise ]

60
00:02:36,088 --> 00:02:37,824
[ Fart noise ]

61
00:02:37,824 --> 00:02:40,426
Uhhh. [ Laughing ]

62
00:02:40,426 --> 00:02:42,128
[ Laughter ]

63
00:02:48,701 --> 00:02:49,835
-So sorry.

64
00:02:49,835 --> 00:02:51,971
Whoever that is, I'm so sorry.

65
00:02:51,971 --> 00:02:53,473
So sorry.

66
00:02:53,473 --> 00:02:55,174
Age is not kind.

67
00:02:55,174 --> 00:02:56,675
Oh, God.
-[ Coughing ]

68
00:02:56,675 --> 00:02:58,678
[ Laughter continues ]

69
00:03:01,647 --> 00:03:03,616
Oh, God.

70
00:03:03,616 --> 00:03:05,184
This is the final round.

71
00:03:05,184 --> 00:03:08,521
[ Laughter ]

72
00:03:08,521 --> 00:03:09,989
-Oh, God. Is it my turn
or your turn?

73
00:03:09,989 --> 00:03:11,958
It's my turn.

74
00:03:11,958 --> 00:03:14,226
[ Laughter ]

75
00:03:14,226 --> 00:03:16,796
-We can watch --
[ Laughing ]

76
00:03:16,796 --> 00:03:18,565
We can watch the video
at the same time.

77
00:03:18,565 --> 00:03:21,300
-I don't think I can stop it.
Okay.

78
00:03:21,300 --> 00:03:22,601
-Okay. Here we go.

79
00:03:22,601 --> 00:03:23,670
Not laughing.

80
00:03:23,670 --> 00:03:25,571
-Grinch. Okay, come on.
-Here we go.

81
00:03:25,571 --> 00:03:27,206
-[ Blows raspberry ]
All right, here we go.

82
00:03:27,206 --> 00:03:28,441
-Go.

83
00:03:28,441 --> 00:03:32,145
[ All chanting "We want Santa" ]

84
00:03:36,615 --> 00:03:38,351
-Where is he?

85
00:03:38,351 --> 00:03:41,554
[ Indistinct shouting ]

86
00:03:41,554 --> 00:03:43,990
[ Laughter ]

87
00:03:43,990 --> 00:03:46,059
[ Applause ]

88
00:03:46,059 --> 00:03:48,093
-Oh, my God!

89
00:03:48,093 --> 00:03:50,930
[ Blows raspberry ]

90
00:03:50,930 --> 00:03:52,231
Dave, can we watch that --

91
00:03:52,231 --> 00:03:54,266
that football --
-Wow.

92
00:03:54,266 --> 00:03:55,735
-Can we watch the football one
one more time?

93
00:03:55,735 --> 00:03:58,471
The football one?
-The football one.

94
00:03:58,471 --> 00:03:59,972
[ Fart noise ]

95
00:03:59,972 --> 00:04:01,707
[ Laughter ]

96
00:04:01,707 --> 00:04:03,076
[ Fart noise ]

97
00:04:04,076 --> 00:04:07,045
[ Cheers and applause ]

98
00:04:07,045 --> 00:04:09,048
-Benedict Cumberbatch!

99
00:04:09,048 --> 00:04:10,216
[ Cheers and applause ]

100
00:04:10,216 --> 00:04:12,051
Stick around -- [ Laughing ]

101
00:04:12,051 --> 00:04:14,887
We'll be right back for more
on "The Tonight Show"!

